member.summary:
public AtomLink FindService(string service,string type)
              Retrieves the first link with the supplied 'rel' and/or 'type' value.
              If either parameter is null, the corresponding match isn't needed.

public AtomLink FindService(string service,string type)
              Retrieves the first link with the supplied 'rel' and/or 'type' value.
              If either parameter is null, the corresponding match isn't needed.
